    "description_long": "This is a compact, vintage-style convertible car with a pastel pink body and a contrasting white hardtop roof. The car features a classic, boxy silhouette with rounded edges, prominent fenders, and a simple front grille. The wheels are small and white-walled, matching the retro aesthetic, and the side mirrors are minimalistic. The windows are tinted dark, and the interior appears to be upholstered in a deep red color. Chrome accents are visible on the bumpers and around the headlights and taillights, enhancing its nostalgic appeal. The rear of the car displays a license plate and small, vertical taillights.",
